          "locales": {
            "en": {
              "text": "<p>I am a <b>Cloud & DevOps Engineer</b> with <b>1+ years of hands-on experience</b> delivering reliable cloud environments and automated release systems. My focus is production readiness, stability, and high deployment confidence.</p><p>I design and maintain <b>CI/CD pipelines</b>, container platforms with <b>Docker + Kubernetes</b>, serverless workloads on <b>AWS</b>, and infrastructure provisioning through <b>Terraform</b>. I also work with monitoring and alerting practices to keep systems observable and resilient.</p><p>I care about measurable outcomes: faster and safer releases, reduced operational risk, improved uptime, and cloud infrastructure that scales cleanly with business needs.</p>"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },

